('53ce3db3-b285-5d3c-909f-106647f843de', '9ac83e0c-f082-405b-889f-c65acd6bcb6f', 'Is he ___ to speak English well?', '他能說好英文嗎？', 'able', 'fast', 'tall', 'cold', 'able 為形容詞，表示「能夠的」。', '記住 be able to + V → 能夠做某事。', '2026-07-06 12:27:27', '2026-07-06 12:27:27'),
